query:
UPDATE subscriptions
            SET
                subscription_name = $1,
                subscription_mailing_address_line_1 = $2,
                subscription_mailing_address_line_2 = $3,
                subscription_city = $4,
                subscription_state = $5,
                subscription_postal_code = $6,
                subscription_email_address = $7
            WHERE id = $8
